    +header('groupoid.svg', 'Groupoid Infinity', 'The Language of Space')
    article.main
        .om
            section
                h1 TRUSTED SYSTEMS
            aside 7 MAY 2018
            p.
                Here is presented the conceptual model of theorem proving system as a set of
                1) calculuses with its categorical models;
                2) programs or base libraries; and
                3) program transformations: type checking, compilation, code erasure, extraction, optimizing, etc.
                The overal system is dedicated for math and general purpose programming
                with code extraction to functional programming language compilers or interpreters.
            section
                h1 STRUCTURE
            p.
                The thesis is grouped by research areas with its corresponding type systems,
                formal models, type checkers and base libraries.
