                h1 TRANSFORMATIONS
            p.
                The process of formal verification is started from model encoding (1),
                then linking with the base library of math components (2),
                then desugaring to pure functions (6),
                then linking with pure base library (3),
                then extracting either to Erlang (4) or Verified Interpreter O (5).
